ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectOrder Authorizing the Modifications to Canada’s Schedule of Specific Commitments Under the General Agreement on Trade in Services
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to take the actions necessary to bring into force for Canada the modifications to Canada’s Schedule of Specific Commitments under the General Agreement on Trade in Services, as set out in the World Trade Organization Reference Paper on Services Domestic Regulation (INF/SDR/2, of November 26, 2021).
